WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
narrator: troubleshooting — the operator-side first-pass triage.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
narrator: a peer reports tailscale up hangs on the login-server URL.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:25.000
narrator: curl /healthz from the affected host isolates DNS or TLS.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:35.000
narrator: the control-plane journal shows the exact rejection reason.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:45.000
narrator: a stale preauth key is the most common cause — mint a fresh one.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:55.000
narrator: for DERP failures, the sidecar logs surface the handshake.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:05.000
narrator: full triage flowchart lives in docs/troubleshooting.md.
